  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tRefrigerator<br />\n\tA refrigerator keeps food at a lowered temperature in order to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/prolong\" target=\"_blank\">prolong</a> its freshness. Where is the refrigerator? What items are in it? Who are the people using the refrigerator?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They opened the door to the refrigerator... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) a huge refrigerator in a restaurant<br />\n\t2) a tiny refrigerator in the room of a student in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dormitory\" target=\"_blank\">dormitory</a><br />\n\t3) the invention of refrigerator<br />\n\t4) police entered a house and opened the refrigerator, discovering something unexpected<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tSeveral dry and wet <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sauna\" target=\"_blank\">sauna</a> rooms were built with different materials, like <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/charcoal\" target=\"_blank\">charcoal</a>, bamboo, salt blocks, promoting various health benefits. There was even an ice room like a refrigerator. Sean was fascinated. He really wanted to jump in and give it a try! Finally, they reached the restaurant which took up the entire floor. Sean was surprised that the fine restaurant was not at the top floor of the building. His host explained that there are hotel rooms and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/penthouse\" target=\"_blank\">penthouse</a> suites on the upper floors. This is not a health club, it's more like a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/resort\" target=\"_blank\">resort</a>, Sean thought to himself.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161844301643/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721245/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721245\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723104/\">英国人教你记单词：22万词汇so easy！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723105/\">中外最强毒舌: 该不该买苹果表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722622/\">英媒: 嫉妒我们车厢空旷才来看地铁帅哥！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723074/\">励志活字典:51岁女教师2年背完22万单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723210/\">王学兵涉毒被抓: 那些吸毒的禁毒大使</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722967/\">村上春树推荐五本必看外国小说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722906/\">求职窍门: 脸书CEO的职业建议</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 